@startuml
actor "Cron_Scheduler" as Cron
participant "AutoConfirm API" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB
participant "Nodemailer" as EM

Cron -> API: GET /api/cron/auto-confirm (Mỗi 2 phút)
API -> DB: find Bookings\n(status: pending, startTime <= now + 1 hours)
DB --> API: targetBookings

loop "Cho mỗi booking"
    API -> DB: update(status = 'confirmed')
    DB --> API: updated
    API -> EM: sendAutoConfirmEmail(user, bookingInfo)
    EM --> API: Email sent
end

API --> Cron: 200 OK (Thống kê số lịch hẹn đã confirm tự động)
@enduml
